description: A landmark collaboration between Salta Properties, Bates Smart, and TCL, Walmer offers a rare lifestyle opportunity on the banks of the Yarra River, where architectural sophistication meets refined luxury. This expansive residence impresses from the outset, with a grand living and dining space framed by floor-to-ceiling glass, bathing the interior in natural light and connecting seamlessly to the outdoors.  Sliding doors open to an oversized terrace, perfect for morning coffees, twilight drinks, or sun-filled entertaining. Panoramic views stretch across verdant bushland, the Yarra River, and the Melbourne skyline.  Designed for the modern entertainer, the gourmet kitchen boasts a Gaggenau suite including an induction cooktop, dual ovens, dishwasher, and a sculptural waterfall island bench. The lavish master suite features a private ensuite and full-height built-in robes, joined by a spacious second bedroom and a sleek central bathroom.  Premium finishes include striking stone surfaces, engineered oak floors, zoned heating and cooling, motorised window furnishings, European laundry, video intercom, one basement car space that is wired and are ready for an electric car charger, and a secure storage cage.  Residents enjoy access to world-class amenities: a 25-metre lap pool, concierge service, wine room, private lounge and dining areas, gym, steam and sauna rooms, car wash and dog wash, wellness room and visitor parking. Ideally located, you're just moments from city trams, Victoria Gardens Shopping Centre, riverside parks and trails, acclaimed cafes, restaurants, bars, and top-tier schools.  **To Inspect**  Please refer to the listed inspection times. If no inspection time is available or you are not able to make the listed time/s please click "Get in Touch" to request an Inspection Time or Contact Agent and register your interest.  **Please Note**  Open for Inspection times and property availability is subject to change without notice. We highly recommend registering for an inspection you are going to attend to avoid disappointment for cancellations. If you are registered for an inspection, you will be notified by SMS if the inspection is cancelled.  **Caution**  Marshall White has exclusive leasing rights to this property. We do not advertise on Gumtree, Facebook Marketplace or any other social media platforms. Please beware of scammers and apply only via the official advertising link using the Snug platform.

description: Nestled in the heart of Abbotsford's highly sought-after enclave, this beautifully renovated Victorian residence offers the perfect blend of timeless character and modern convenience. Surrounded by the meandering Yarra River trails, extensive parklands, vibrant cafés, restaurants, arts precincts, and eclectic shopping, the lifestyle on offer here is unmatched. With Collingwood Train Station nearby and the CBD or MCG within easy reach by foot or cycle, this home presents an address of absolute convenience.  Behind its charming, laced veranda and classic picket fence, the home opens to soaring Victorian ceilings and freshly painted interiors that highlight its elegant transformation. Brand new timber floorboards lead the way through to two generous robed bedrooms, each enhanced by double-glazed windows and quality insulation for year-round comfort and efficiency. The sleek kitchen showcases stone benchtops, premium cabinetry and gas cooking, while the stunning bathroom impresses with floor-to-ceiling tiles, excellent storage and a large shower.  A split system heating and cooling unit ensures modern comfort and a private sunlit courtyard provides the ideal space to enjoy a quiet morning.  Positioned within moments of schools, transport, cycling paths, major arterials, and the acclaimed Carringbush Hotel, this enchanting Victorian home epitomises inner-city living at its finest. Renovated to perfection while retaining its heritage charm, it promises an enviable lifestyle in one of Melbourne's most dynamic locations. Note: gas fireplace has been disconnected.  **To Inspect**  Please refer to the listed inspection times. description: Discover this spacious and beautifully appointed two bedroom home, perfectly located in one of Abbotsford's most sought-after pockets. The home features a well-equipped kitchen and meals area complete with quality appliances, a gas cooktop, oven, ample cupboard space, and split system heating and cooling. The space seamlessly connects to a separate living area, also fitted with split system heating and cooling, and access to a private courtyard - ideal for alfresco entertaining or quiet relaxation. Both bedrooms are generously sized and include built-in robes, while the bright bathroom at the rear of the home includes a shower-over-bath and convenient laundry facilities. Stylish floorboards throughout complete the home's modern appeal. Enjoy unbeatable access to North Richmond Station, city-bound trams, and an abundance of cafes, restaurants, and shops along vibrant Victoria Street. An inspection is a must! The Tenant should make their own enquiries with the municipal council in regard to any such car parking before signing this Agreement.  Would you like to Inspect this property? description: The property is subject to the presence of physical objects. Photos are for reference purposes only and may not reflect the current state of the property.  Experience the perfect blend of cosmopolitan living and serene tranquility in this state-of-the-art, 2-bedroom apartment in the prestigious 'Green Square' development. Positioned adjacent to the picturesque banks of the Yarra River, this residence offers supreme urban convenience in a remarkable location.  Immerse yourself in sleek sophistication and impressive style as you discover the harmonious balance between the vibrant Victoria Street restaurant scene and the calming ambiance of the Yarra River. Moreover, with Victoria Gardens shopping just across the road, this lifestyle combination is truly unparalleled.  Step inside this sleek and sophisticated apartment, where style takes center stage. The spacious kitchen exudes elegance, boasting tasteful European appliances and smooth stone benchtops.  The open plan living and dining area effortlessly flows outdoors to a large, enclosed balcony, offering stunning views of the surrounding urban landscape. This private sanctuary is perfect for relaxation or entertaining.  The master bedroom exudes elegance and functionality, featuring built-in robes and a stylish ensuite. The second bedroom, also boasting built-in robes, is serviced by the central bathroom.  Embrace a resort-like lifestyle with access to the building's array of amenities, including a swimming pool, gym, library, meeting room, and BBQ area-perfect for entertaining guests. Additional highlights of this exceptional apartment include secure basement parking, a storage cage, intercom entry, a European laundry, and split-system heating and air conditioning, ensuring your comfort and convenience.  Venture down Victoria Street and discover a plethora of exquisite Vietnamese cuisine that rivals the finest offerings in Vietnam itself. Just across the road, Victoria Gardens awaits, offering a wide selection of shops and cinemas for your enjoyment.  City-bound trams are conveniently located at your doorstep, providing easy access to the bustling heart of Melbourne. For natur enthusiasts, the meandering Yarra River with its scenic trails, parklands, and abundant birdlife is just a few meters away, inviting you to explore its natural beauty.

description: Set across three expansive levels, this four-bedroom, four-bathroom townhouse is a striking blend of contemporary design and adaptable living.  The upper level is devoted to light-filled living, where the dining and kitchen zones connect seamlessly to a flexible room that may serve as a fourth bedroom, home office, children's retreat or additional sitting room.   The kitchen is beautifully appointed with modern appliances, including gas cooking and a dishwasher, while double-glazed windows and reverse-cycle heating and cooling ensure year-round comfort. Two private terraces extend the living spaces outdoors.  On the middle level, two generously sized bedrooms each enjoy their own bathrooms, one as a private en suite and the other complemented by a central bathroom, both with access to outdoor areas.   The ground floor features secure garage parking for one car, a European laundry, and a sizable courtyard. A fourth bedroom on this level is complete with built-in robes and its own en suite, creating an ideal retreat for guests or extended family.  With its thoughtful design, four bathrooms, and flexible layout, this home is perfectly tailored for modern living. All just a short stroll to Abbotsford's acclaimed cafés, restaurants and excellent public transport links.  **If this property is of interest to you, please ensure that you register your interest by clicking on the 'Get in touch' button, so that you are kept up to date with inspections, price changes and similar properties that may be suitable.
